@startuml 时序图_WebSocket消息
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title WebSocket消息发送时序图

actor "家长A" as UserA
actor "管理员" as Admin
participant "浏览器A" as BrowserA
participant "浏览器B" as BrowserB
participant "SocketIO\n服务器" as SocketIO
database "SQLite\nmessages表" as DB

== 连接建立 ==
UserA -> BrowserA: 打开消息中心
BrowserA -> SocketIO: connect
SocketIO -> SocketIO: 验证Session
SocketIO -> SocketIO: join_room('user_A')
SocketIO --> BrowserA: emit 'connected'

Admin -> BrowserB: 打开消息中心
BrowserB -> SocketIO: connect
SocketIO -> SocketIO: join_room('admin')
SocketIO --> BrowserB: emit 'connected'

== 发送消息 ==
UserA -> BrowserA: 输入消息，点击发送
BrowserA -> SocketIO: emit 'send_message' {message, room}
SocketIO -> SocketIO: 校验内容（非空、<=500字符）
SocketIO -> SocketIO: 校验房间白名单

SocketIO -> DB: INSERT messages (sender_id=A, receiver_id=admin)
DB --> SocketIO: 插入成功

SocketIO -> BrowserB: emit 'new_message' to room='admin'
BrowserB --> Admin: 实时显示新消息
BrowserB -> BrowserB: 播放提示音/未读标记

== 已读回执 ==
Admin -> BrowserB: 打开与A的对话
BrowserB -> SocketIO: GET /api/conversation/A
SocketIO -> DB: UPDATE messages SET status='read' WHERE receiver=admin AND sender=A
SocketIO -> DB: SELECT * FROM messages WHERE (sender=A AND receiver=admin) OR (sender=admin AND receiver=A)
DB --> SocketIO: messages[]
SocketIO --> BrowserB: JSON {messages}
BrowserB --> Admin: 显示历史消息

== 管理员回复 ==
Admin -> BrowserB: 输入回复，发送
BrowserB -> SocketIO: POST /send_message
SocketIO -> DB: INSERT messages (sender=admin, receiver=A)
SocketIO -> BrowserA: emit 'new_message'
BrowserA --> UserA: 实时接收回复

@enduml